Football is played with several key pieces of equipments:

1. Football
2. Football boots
3. Shin guards
4. Jersey
5. Shorts
6. Socks
7. Goalkeeper gloves
8. Goalposts and Crossbar
9. Nets
10.Corner flags
11. Whistle
12. Referee's cards
13. Linesman flag
14. Training cones and markers
15. Medical kit

